161
00:06:59,458 --> 00:07:01,208
We all share a common goal.

162
00:07:01,958 --> 00:07:03,917
Here you are, Kita.

163
00:07:04,958 --> 00:07:07,125
Yes, yes.

164
00:07:07,125 --> 00:07:08,167
It is I, the come-and-go,

165
00:07:08,167 --> 00:07:09,542
"SAKURA BAKUSHIN O"
Sakura Bakushin O.

166
00:07:10,333 --> 00:07:12,708
See you later, Kita.

167
00:07:13,167 --> 00:07:14,792
Diamond, wait for me!

168
00:07:14,792 --> 00:07:16,292
After your debut,

169
00:07:16,292 --> 00:07:19,042
