340
00:16:00,500 --> 00:16:02,500
So, I…

341
00:16:03,042 --> 00:16:04,500
"SPECIAL TAIYAKI"
Two taiyakis, please.

342
00:16:04,500 --> 00:16:05,625
"SPECIAL TAIYAKI"
Custard and…

343
00:16:05,625 --> 00:16:06,917
"SPECIAL TAIYAKI"
Custard for both.

344
00:16:09,458 --> 00:16:12,667
The Japanese Derby will begin soon.

345
00:16:12,667 --> 00:16:16,792
How will the horse girls perform?
What will happen?

346
00:16:16,792 --> 00:16:19,750
We are all waiting for the answers.

347
00:16:19,750 --> 00:16:20,792
Mr. Yamamoto.

348
00:16:20,792 --> 00:16:22,542
