Enjoy the nervousness too.

361
00:16:54,792 --> 00:16:55,750
Kita.

362
00:16:57,000 --> 00:16:58,958
Be yourself, okay?

363
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:02,000
Yes!

364
00:17:02,500 --> 00:17:05,167
Here she is,
the highly-anticipated horse girl.

365
00:17:05,583 --> 00:17:06,708
"DURAMENTE, PREVIOUSLY ON SATSUKI SHO"
She won Satsuki Sho

366
00:17:06,708 --> 00:17:08,792
