the champion of horse girls,

390
00:18:38,042 --> 00:18:40,375
Tokyo Yushun, Japanese Derby.

391
00:18:40,375 --> 00:18:42,000
18 horse girls, each carrying a dream

392
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:44,292
on their shoulders

