00:18:44,292 --> 00:18:46,625
enter the starting gate.

394
00:18:47,625 --> 00:18:49,750
Everything is in position now.

395
00:18:49,750 --> 00:18:51,667
May destiny lead them to their glory.

396
00:18:51,667 --> 00:18:54,625
No, they will earn glory with sheer will!

397
00:18:54,625 --> 00:18:56,375
Start!

398
00:18:56,375 --> 00:18:58,792
6 had a later start,

399
00:18:58,792 --> 00:19:01,208
but everyone was off to a great start.

400
00:19:01,208 --> 00:19:03,958
Which one of them will reach
the spectator's stand first?

401
00:19:03,958 --> 00:19:05,375
-Go!
-Will it be

402
00:19:05,375 --> 00:19:06,292
America Spike?

403
00:19:06,292 --> 00:19:09,250
Kitasan Black approached the middle now.

404
00:19:09,250 --> 00:19:10,500
Ribbon Pia is in the lead,

405
00:19:10,500 --> 00:19:12,042
