part, the first bend.

411
00:19:26,333 --> 00:19:28,708
The luckiest one
will always win the Derby.

412
00:19:28,708 --> 00:19:31,375
Such as Eishin Flash,
Tanino Gimlet, and Special Week.

413
00:19:31,375 --> 00:19:34,667
Records show it's usually won
by the third place of Satsuki Sho.

414
00:19:34,667 --> 00:19:35,750
Why is that?

415
00:19:35,750 --> 00:19:38,167
Do you know who is the third place
in this year's Satsuki Sho?

416
00:19:38,167 --> 00:19:40,083
That's right. It's Kitasan Black.

417
00:19:41,958 --> 00:19:43,333
I see.

418
00:19:43,333 --> 00:19:46,125
