in the Tokyo Racecourse.

428
00:20:07,167 --> 00:20:09,792
She's the only one ahead of me.

429
00:20:09,792 --> 00:20:12,625
I can see the finishing line now.

430
00:20:12,625 --> 00:20:14,417
We are now at the fourth bend.

431
00:20:14,417 --> 00:20:18,000
After this is the final stretch.

432
00:20:18,000 --> 00:20:20,208
Everything is at stake.

433
00:20:20,208 --> 00:20:21,083
-I can do this.
-Everything is at stake.

434
00:20:21,083 --> 00:20:22,583
-From here to the finishing line…
-The final stretch of this race.

435
00:20:22,583 --> 00:20:23,333
-I have to win.
-The final stretch of this race.

436
00:20:23,333 --> 00:20:24,625
-I must win.
-Go.

437
00:20:24,625 --> 00:20:27,292
Kitasan Black and Ribbon
are going neck and neck.

438
00:20:27,292 --> 00:20:29,833
Go!

439
00:20:29,833 --> 00:20:31,958
Ribbon will not concede either.

440
00:20:31,958 --> 00:20:34,042
