442
00:20:37,875 --> 00:20:39,792
Kitasan Black is still chasing.

443
00:20:39,792 --> 00:20:42,458
Will one of them win this race?

444
00:20:42,458 --> 00:20:43,958
But it's too early to say.

445
00:20:43,958 --> 00:20:45,958
This long final stretch

446
00:20:45,958 --> 00:20:48,708
is their one-way ticket to glory.

447
00:20:48,708 --> 00:20:52,000
18 horse girls are giving their all.

448
00:20:53,333 --> 00:20:54,792
Here she is.

449
00:20:54,792 --> 00:20:57,000
Duramente accelerated.

450
00:20:57,000 --> 00:20:59,833
I won't lose. The fight is just starting!

451
00:20:59,833 --> 00:21:02,708
The final 200 meters!

452
00:21:09,458 --> 00:21:13,167
Duramente is in the lead.

453
00:21:13,917 --> 00:21:16,083
No. The finishing line is not here yet.

454
00:21:16,083 --> 00:21:20,208
Duramente takes the lead!

455
00:21:20,833 --> 00:21:23,042
Duramente!

456
00:21:23,833 --> 00:21:25,875
Duramente!

457
00:21:25,875 --> 00:21:27,583
She is so fast.

458
00:21:27,583 --> 00:21:30,542
She overtook everyone.

459
00:21:30,542 --> 00:21:34,792
Duramente got two crowns!

460
00:21:34,792 --> 00:21:37,667
No one can stop her!

461
00:21:37,667 --> 00:21:40,000
